Cell["\<\
The emission or absorption spectra of atoms can in part be explained by the \
concepts we have already discussed: the observed spectral lines correspond to \
a change in the energy eigenstate of an electron and the corresponding \
emission or absorption of light. These transitions are illustrated in a \
simplified manner for sodium in Figure 8.3. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9183812032367754`*^9, 3.9183814878059826`*^9}, 
   3.9183825635773993`*^9, {3.918382598926309*^9, 3.9183826241746864`*^9}, {
   3.918382944502144*^9, 
   3.918382947558114*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8ceade2e-9ce0-47a7-a1e8-\
2314524f2e5f"],

