   3.9184032181888733`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5c0a21df-1449-4f41-8c02-\
4db3fdfbd133"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "and the magnitude of the ",
 StyleBox["z ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "component of the orbital angular momentum given by"
}], "Text",
